<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>My Store Manager — Made Easy for Your Store</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,300&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --navy:    #0c1123;
      --navy2:   #111829;
      --navy3:   #192038;
      --navy4:   #1e2848;
      --blue:    #4f8ef7;
      --blue2:   #2563eb;
      --teal:    #34d98b;
      --amber:   #f59e0b;
      --red:     #f7614f;
      --purple:  #9b7cf7;
      --text:    #dde3f4;
      --muted:   #6b7799;
      --dimmer:  #3d4a6a;
      --border:  rgba(79,142,247,0.12);
      --border2: rgba(79,142,247,0.24);
      --glow:    rgba(79,142,247,0.2);
      --font:    'Inter', sans-serif;
      --mono:    'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    }

    html, body { height: 100%; overflow-x: hidden; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font);
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── GRID BACKGROUND ── */
    .grid-bg {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(79,142,247,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(79,142,247,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
    }

    /* ── AMBIENT ORBS ── */
    .orb {
      position: fixed; border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    }
    .orb1 {
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(79,142,247,0.09) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: -180px; left: -140px;
    }
    .orb2 {
      width: 450px; height: 450px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,217,139,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      bottom: -80px; right: -80px;
    }
    .orb3 {
      width: 300px; height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(155,124,247,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: 40%; right: 20%;
    }

    .page-wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }

    /* ════════════════════════════
       NAVIGATION
    ════════════════════════════ */
    nav {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 52px; height: 64px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(12,17,35,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 200;
    }
    .logo-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-decoration: none; }
    .logo-name {
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.04em; color: var(--text); line-height: 1;
    }
    .logo-name span { color: var(--blue); }
    .logo-tagline {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .nav-signin {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none; padding: 7px 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border2); border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-signin:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: rgba(79,142,247,0.5); }
    .nav-cta {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none; padding: 8px 20px;
      background: var(--blue); border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(79,142,247,0.3);
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ════════════════════════════
       HERO
    ════════════════════════════ */
    .hero {
      flex: 1;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 64px 52px 40px;
      gap: 48px;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
    }

    /* ── LEFT TEXT ── */
    .hero-left { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both; }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(79,142,247,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(79,142,247,0.22);
      border-radius: 100px; padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--blue);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .pulse-dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal);
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: 56px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -0.045em; margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .hero-h1 .accent { color: var(--blue); }
    .hero-h1 .light  { font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); font-size: 48px; }
    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.78;
      max-width: 460px; margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-pills {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .pill {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
      background: var(--navy2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 100px; padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .pill:hover { border-color: var(--border2); color: var(--text); }
    .pill .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: var(--blue); color: #fff; text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 30px;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(79,142,247,0.38);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 36px rgba(79,142,247,0.5); }
    .btn-ghost {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      color: var(--text); text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 26px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--blue); }
    .trust-row {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 36px; padding-top: 28px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .trust-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--dimmer);
    }
    .trust-item svg { color: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* ── RIGHT / ANIMATED SCENE ── */
    .hero-right {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.2s both;
    }

    /* ════════════════════════════
       SCENE
    ════════════════════════════ */
    .scene {
      position: relative;
      width: 520px; height: 540px;
    }

    /* ── LAPTOP ── */
    .laptop-wrap {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 60px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-52%);
      z-index: 4;
    }
    .laptop-screen {
      width: 210px; height: 138px;
      background: var(--navy4);
      border: 2px solid rgba(79,142,247,0.35);
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(79,142,247,0.18), inset 0 0 20px rgba(79,142,247,0.05);
    }
    .screen-inner { padding: 10px 12px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .screen-topbar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .sdot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .screen-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 7px; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 5px; }
    .sbar {
      height: 6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 5px;
      animation: barPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    .sbar.s1 { width: 80%; background: rgba(79,142,247,0.55); }
    .sbar.s2 { width: 58%; background: rgba(52,217,139,0.45); animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .sbar.s3 { width: 68%; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.4);  animation-delay: 0.7s; }
    .sbar.s4 { width: 48%; background: rgba(155,124,247,0.4); animation-delay: 1.1s; }
    .snums { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-top: 8px; }
    .snum {
      background: rgba(79,142,247,0.15); border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 2px 6px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 7px; color: var(--blue);
    }
    .screen-glow {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 110%, rgba(79,142,247,0.25) 0%, transparent 60%);
      animation: glowPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .laptop-base {
      width: 230px; height: 14px; margin-left: -10px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--navy4), var(--navy3));
      border: 2px solid rgba(79,142,247,0.25); border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    /* Blue emergence glow from laptop hinge */
    .laptop-emerge-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 90px; height: 28px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(79,142,247,0.55) 0%, transparent 75%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: emergePulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    /* ── GENIE ── */
    .genie-wrap {
      position: absolute;
      /* Positioned so genie appears to float above the laptop center */
      bottom: 195px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-58%);
      z-index: 6;
      animation: genieEmerge 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.5, 0.64, 1) 0.3s both,
                 genieFloat   3.5s ease-in-out 2s infinite;
      transform-origin: bottom center;
    }
    .genie-svg {
      width: 155px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 18px rgba(79,142,247,0.45))
              drop-shadow(0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
    }
    /* Smoke ribbon rising from laptop */
    .smoke-base {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -15px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 14px; height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(79,142,247,0.5), rgba(79,142,247,0.1), transparent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: smokeRise 1.5s ease-out 0.3s both;
      filter: blur(5px);
    }
    /* Sparkle dots around genie */
    .sp {
      position: absolute; border-radius: 50%;
      animation: sparkleTwinkle 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .sp1 { width:9px; height:9px; background:var(--teal);   top:22px; left:-14px; animation-delay:0s;   box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--teal); }
    .sp2 { width:7px; height:7px; background:var(--amber);  top:55px; right:-12px;animation-delay:0.6s; box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--amber); }
    .sp3 { width:6px; height:6px; background:var(--blue);   top:8px;  right:14px; animation-delay:1.1s; box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--blue); }
    .sp4 { width:8px; height:8px; background:var(--purple); bottom:15px;left:-8px;animation-delay:0.9s; box-shadow:0 0 9px var(--purple); }
    .sp5 { width:5px; height:5px; background:var(--teal);   bottom:30px;right:-5px;animation-delay:1.6s;box-shadow:0 0 7px var(--teal); }

    /* ── STOREKEEPER ── */
    .keeper-wrap {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 32px; right: 12px;
      z-index: 5;
      animation: keeperSlideIn 1s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.3,0.64,1) 0.7s both,
                 keeperBob     4.5s ease-in-out 2s infinite;
    }
    .keeper-svg {
      width: 210px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.45));
    }
    /* Speech bubble above keeper */
    .keeper-bubble {
      position: absolute;
      top: -6px; left: -108px;
      background: var(--navy3);
      border: 1px solid rgba(52,217,139,0.3);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--text); white-space: nowrap;
      animation: bubblePop 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1) 2.6s both;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }
    .keeper-bubble::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -7px; right: 22px;
      width: 12px; height: 12px;
      background: var(--navy3);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(52,217,139,0.3);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(52,217,139,0.3);
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    /* ── FLOATING METRIC CARDS ── */
    .mcard {
      position: absolute; z-index: 7;
      background: rgba(15,22,42,0.88);
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }
    .mc-lbl { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .mc-val { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--mono); }
    .mc-sub { font-size: 10px; margin-top: 3px; }
    .mc-up   { color: var(--teal); }
    .mc-warn { color: var(--amber); }
    .mc-blue { color: var(--blue); }

    .mcard-sales { top: 18px; left: 8px;  animation: floatCard1 5s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .mcard-stock { top: 32px; right: 8px; animation: floatCard2 4.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.7s; }
    .mcard-gst   { bottom: 230px; left: 18px; animation: floatCard3 6s ease-in-out infinite 1.3s; }

    /* ── SVG DATA ARC ── */
    .arc-svg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 3;
      overflow: visible;
    }

    /* ════════════════════════════
       FEATURES STRIP
    ════════════════════════════ */
    .features {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    }
    .feat {
      padding: 28px 26px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .feat:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .feat:hover { background: var(--navy2); }
    .feat-icon {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 9px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .fi-blue   { background: rgba(79,142,247,0.12); }
    .fi-teal   { background: rgba(52,217,139,0.12); }
    .fi-amber  { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); }
    .fi-coral  { background: rgba(247,97,79,0.12); }
    .fi-purple { background: rgba(155,124,247,0.12); }
    .feat-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .feat-desc  { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ════════════════════════════
       KEYFRAMES
    ════════════════════════════ */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(28px); }
      to   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100% { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
      50%      { opacity:0.4; transform:scale(0.7); }
    }
    @keyframes barPulse {
      from { opacity: 0.45; }
      to   { opacity: 1; }
    }
    @keyframes glowPulse {
      from { opacity: 0.5; }
      to   { opacity: 1; }
    }
    @keyframes emergePulse {
      from { opacity:0.4; transform:translateX(-50%) scale(0.85); }
      to   { opacity:1;   transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1.2); }
    }
    @keyframes genieEmerge {
      0%   { opacity:0; transform:translateX(-58%) translateY(100px) scale(0.25); }
      25%  { opacity:1; transform:translateX(-58%) translateY(30px)  scale(0.7); }
      60%  { transform:translateX(-58%) translateY(-10px) scale(1.04); }
      100% { opacity:1; transform:translateX(-58%) translateY(0px)   scale(1); }
    }
    @keyframes genieFloat {
      0%,100% { transform:translateX(-58%) translateY(0px)   rotate(-2deg); }
      50%      { transform:translateX(-58%) translateY(-14px) rotate(2deg); }
    }
    @keyframes smokeRise {
      0%   { opacity:0; transform:translateX(-50%) scaleY(0); }
      100% { opacity:1; transform:translateX(-50%) scaleY(1); }
    }
    @keyframes sparkleTwinkle {
      0%,100% { opacity:0; transform:scale(0.4); }
      50%      { opacity:1; transform:scale(1.4); }
    }
    @keyframes keeperSlideIn {
      from { opacity:0; transform:translateX(40px); }
      to   { opacity:1; transform:translateX(0); }
    }
    @keyframes keeperBob {
      0%,100% { transform:translateY(0px); }
      50%      { transform:translateY(-7px); }
    }
    @keyframes bubblePop {
      from { opacity:0; transform:scale(0.4); }
      to   { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
    }
    @keyframes floatCard1 {
      0%,100% { transform:translate(0,0) rotate(-1deg); }
      50%      { transform:translate(3px,-10px) rotate(0.5deg); }
    }
    @keyframes floatCard2 {
      0%,100% { transform:translate(0,0) rotate(1deg); }
      50%      { transform:translate(-3px,-8px) rotate(-0.5deg); }
    }
    @keyframes floatCard3 {
      0%,100% { transform:translate(0,0) rotate(-0.5deg); }
      50%      { transform:translate(4px,-9px) rotate(0.5deg); }
    }

    /* ════════════════════════════
       RESPONSIVE
    ════════════════════════════ */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns:1fr; min-height:auto; padding:40px 24px 32px; }
      .hero-right { display:none; }
      .hero-h1 { font-size:38px; }
      .hero-h1 .light { font-size:32px; }
      nav { padding:0 20px; }
      .nav-links { display:none; }
      .features { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
      .feat:nth-child(4) { border-right:none; }
      .feat:last-child { grid-column:span 2; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="grid-bg"></div>
<div class="orb orb1"></div>
<div class="orb orb2"></div>
<div class="orb orb3"></div>

<div class="page-wrap">

  <!-- ══════════ NAVIGATION ══════════ -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="logo-wrap">
      <div class="logo-name">My<span>Store</span> Manager</div>
      <div class="logo-tagline">Made easy for your store</div>
    </a>

    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
      <li><a href="#reports">Reports</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Pricing</a></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="nav-actions">
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: "nav-signin" %>
      <%= link_to "Get Started →", new_user_session_path, class: "nav-cta" %>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
  <section class="hero">

    <!-- LEFT: TEXT -->
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <div class="pulse-dot"></div>
        Store Management &middot; Made Easy
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero-h1">
        Your Store,<br>
        <span class="accent">Runs Smart.</span><br>
        <span class="light">You Just Thrive.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-desc">
        Bills, inventory, accounts, taxes — all managed by one intelligent platform.
        While the genie handles your numbers, you focus on what matters most:
        growing your business.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-pills">
        <div class="pill"><div class="dot"></div>Sales &amp; Purchase Bills</div>
        <div class="pill"><div class="dot"></div>Stock / Inventory</div>
        <div class="pill"><div class="dot"></div>GST &amp; Taxation</div>
        <div class="pill"><div class="dot"></div>Full Reports</div>
        <div class="pill"><div class="dot"></div>Business Insights</div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-btns">
        <%= link_to new_user_session_path, class: "btn-primary" do %>
          Get Started Free
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        <% end %>
        <a href="#features" class="btn-ghost">
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"/>
          </svg>
          See Features
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-row">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
          256-bit Encrypted
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          GST Compliant
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          Multi-tenant
